WEBVTT

00:05.412 --> 00:06.544
__

00:06.580 --> 00:08.830
<i>I think you intend</i>
<i>to return to that beach,</i>

00:08.882 --> 00:11.082
<i>and seize every last ounce</i>
<i>of gold off of it,</i>

00:11.134 --> 00:13.501
and I think you're going
to need my help to do it.

00:13.553 --> 00:17.722
I have committed men and resources
to aid you in retrieving the Urca gold,

00:17.757 --> 00:19.340
<i>in exchange for which</i>
<i>you assured me,</i>

00:19.392 --> 00:21.142
<i>expelling Captain Vane</i>
<i>from that fort.</i>

00:21.177 --> 00:22.177
<i>We'll procure a ship,</i>

00:22.229 --> 00:23.428
we'll recruit men,

00:23.480 --> 00:25.897
<i>and we'll create from nothing,</i>
<i>a new crew.</i>

00:25.932 --> 00:27.315
<i>You asked for better captains.</i>

00:27.350 --> 00:28.933
<i>I give you Captain Jack Rackham.</i>

00:28.985 --> 00:30.435
<i>I can't be your wife, Jack.</i>

00:30.447 --> 00:31.687
You and I are gonna be partners

00:31.688 --> 00:33.688
<i>till they put us in the ground.</i>

00:33.690 --> 00:35.440
<i>That is the crown jewel taken</i>

00:35.492 --> 00:37.275
<i>from the good fortune prize.</i>

00:37.327 --> 00:39.027
Her father's Lord Peter Ashe,

00:39.029 --> 00:40.778
<i>governor of the Carolina Colony.</i>

00:40.830 --> 00:42.997
Her father is a very influential man,

00:43.033 --> 00:44.415
<i>he and I were friends.</i>

00:44.451 --> 00:45.783
<i>When you return her</i>
<i>to her father,</i>

00:45.835 --> 00:46.918
<i>you're going to explain</i>

00:46.953 --> 00:48.703
what it is you're trying
to accomplish here.

00:48.705 --> 00:50.505
<i>A Nassau that can self-govern.</i>

00:50.540 --> 00:52.040
You are no longer a hostage.

00:52.042 --> 00:53.341
I'm gonna get you out of here.

00:53.376 --> 00:56.794
You will turn on absolutely
anyone, won't you?

00:56.846 --> 00:57.886
<i>Listen to me clearly.</i>

00:57.931 --> 01:00.098
<i>You will hear from me again.</i>

01:00.133 --> 01:01.933
You think there's something
valuable enough to make

01:01.968 --> 01:04.769
the British Navy forget that
you and I are pirates?

01:04.804 --> 01:06.387
Not what, who.

01:06.389 --> 01:08.723
<i>This is Eleanor Guthrie,</i>
<i>the trade boss in Nassau.</i>

01:08.775 --> 01:10.558
Imagine sir,
how London would react

01:10.610 --> 01:12.860
to the arrival
of the queen of thieves.

01:12.896 --> 01:14.228
I am so very sorry for what...

01:14.281 --> 01:16.731
- You destroyed our lives!
- Miranda...

01:16.733 --> 01:19.033
<i>I want to see that</i>
<i>noose around your neck,</i>

01:19.069 --> 01:20.190
<i>and I want to pull the lever</i>

01:20.203 --> 01:22.370
with my own two ha...!

01:22.405 --> 01:24.572
<i>I have placed</i>
<i>Captain Flint under arrest!</i>

01:24.624 --> 01:27.458
<i>His trial will be swift and final!</i>

01:27.494 --> 01:29.544
Flint stole from me,
and I'm making it right.

01:29.579 --> 01:32.163
<i>You hate Flint, I hate Flint.</i>

01:32.215 --> 01:35.083
But right now, he's talking
about how we survive,

01:35.135 --> 01:36.217
what comes next.

01:36.252 --> 01:39.003
I suggest we get him
the hell out of there.

01:39.055 --> 01:41.089
Everyone is a monster to someone.

01:41.091 --> 01:43.391
<i>Since you are so convinced</i>
<i>that I am yours,</i>

01:43.426 --> 01:44.726
I will be it.

01:44.761 --> 01:46.227
<i>What are you doing here?</i>

01:46.262 --> 01:48.596
Figured if anyone was going
to make a trophy of you,

01:48.648 --> 01:49.931
<i>it really ought to be me.</i>

01:55.071 --> 01:58.773
Her word
will be the last word for this place.

01:59.659 --> 02:01.442
<i>My men will need</i>
<i>to lean on something solid.</i>

02:01.494 --> 02:02.777
<i>They look to me for that,</i>

02:02.779 --> 02:05.530
but they'll also look
to their new quartermaster.

02:05.582 --> 02:07.415
There's something you ought to know,

02:07.450 --> 02:11.619
<i>before my misfortune at</i>
<i>the hands of Vane's leftenants,</i>

02:11.621 --> 02:14.205
<i>our friend, the scout,</i>
<i>confessed something to me.</i>

02:14.257 --> 02:16.541
<i>He told me that he could</i>
<i>sell the gold's location</i>

02:16.593 --> 02:20.345
<i>to another crew in exchange</i>
<i>for a larger share of the prize.</i>

